Package dxf2svg.util.wiretrace

Class Summary
CrossSheetWireIDs This class provides context for an SVG search.
FindApplyWireIDsStrategy This algorithm seeks the first text from the opposite end of the 'SHEET n[n]' pattern and gives the wire that the text appears over, that wire number as an ID attribute.
FindSheetLinkLabelsStrategy This algorithm searches for sheet(s) matches like: 'SHEET n[n]'.
FindWiresNearestLinkStrategy This algorithm takes the matched sheet(s) and searches for matching polyline wires (or gangs) nearby.
WireLabelLocation This class encapsulates an SvgObject which should be a wire (or gang) and stores it and the integer value or either WireLabelLocation.START_POINT or WireLabelLocation.END_POINT of where the label can be found.
WireSearchStrategy Super class of the search strategies for wires.
